PeopleAlertDialog

public static final int PeopleAlertDialog
this style will be used for every Alert Dialog created in the People application. All AlertDialogs should be created using PeopleAlertDialog but in some cases (e.g. context menus) - the standard AlertDialog is still created. Should be used with PeopleWhiteTheme.Dialog.Alert

PeopleWhiteTheme_Dialog

public static final int PeopleWhiteTheme_Dialog
custom style for the themes Dialog styles The window background is set here so that it will be used instead of android:alertDialogStyle. When using this theme with an AlertDialog class ensure that android:alertDialogStyle points to PeopleDialog style

See Also:
Constant Field Values

PeopleWhiteTheme_Dialog_Alert

public static final int PeopleWhiteTheme_Dialog_Alert
The window background is set to transparent for this theme so that android:alertDialogStyle can be used to draw the dialog background. In this case ensure android:alertDialogStyle points to PeopleAlertDialog
